<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:25:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国预计未来五年城镇化率接近70%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国务院周三表示，预计未来五年常住人口城镇化率将提高到接近70%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>苹果可能会公布更高的收入，因为折扣有助于 iPhone 在中国的需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-post-higher-revenue-discounts-aid-iphone-demand-china-2024-07-31/</link><description>苹果公司可能会在周四报告称，该公司第三财季的收入恢复增长，因为该公司通过大幅iPhone折扣赢得了中国的一些客户，并凭借更新的设计销售了更多高利润的iPad。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:19:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-post-higher-revenue-discounts-aid-iphone-demand-china-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国拖累和北美需求放缓，万豪下调了 2024 年销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-narrows-2024-revenue-growth-forecast-weakening-domestic-tourism-us-2024-07-31/</link><description>酒店运营商万豪国际集团周三下调了对 2024 年客房收入增长的预测，理由是中国经营环境疲软以及北美需求疲软的预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:17:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-narrows-2024-revenue-growth-forecast-weakening-domestic-tourism-us-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>优步与比亚迪合作将电动汽车引入全球网约车平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/uber-byd-partner-bring-evs-ride-hailing-platform-globally-2024-07-31/</link><description>Uber 和中国汽车制造商比亚迪周三宣布建立多年合作伙伴关系，旨在为全球打车平台提供 10 万辆新电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/uber-byd-partner-bring-evs-ride-hailing-platform-globally-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国指责美国议员麦戈文干涉并实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-accuses-us-lawmaker-mcgovern-interference-imposes-sanctions-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国外交部表示，中国以干涉中国内政为由对美国议员吉姆·麦戈文实施制裁，冻结其资产并禁止他在中国进行交易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:43:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-accuses-us-lawmaker-mcgovern-interference-imposes-sanctions-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>GE医疗保健因中国问题下调2024年收入增长预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/ge-healthcare-cuts-2024-organic-sales-growth-forecast-shares-fall-2024-07-31/</link><description>GE医疗集团周三下调了今年的收入增长预期，原因是中国医疗保健行业因反腐败运动而陷入冻结，拖累了其成像设备和其他医疗设备的销售，导致其股价下跌10%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:36:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/ge-healthcare-cuts-2024-organic-sales-growth-forecast-shares-fall-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国开发商世茂的清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/hong-kong-court-adjourns-china-developer-shimaos-liquidation-petition-2024-07-31/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商世茂集团周三表示，香港法院已将该公司的清算听证会推迟至8月12日，从而使其有更多时间与债权人就修订后的重组方案进行合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:18:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/hong-kong-court-adjourns-china-developer-shimaos-liquidation-petition-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行加息，美联储提前加息，大型科技股表现不佳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-31/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>德国指责中国对制图机构进行2021年网络攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-summons-chinese-ambassador-over-2021-cyberattack-cartography-agency-2024-07-31/</link><description>德国周三指责中国幕后策划了 2021 年针对联邦制图机构的网络攻击，以从事间谍活动，并召见北京大使前往柏林提出申诉。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-summons-chinese-ambassador-over-2021-cyberattack-cartography-agency-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>ASML 希望能在下一轮中美芯片大战中幸免于难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-up-hopes-it-will-be-spared-next-round-us-china-chip-fight-2024-07-31/</link><description>最大的电脑芯片制造设备制造商阿斯麦 (ASML) 股价周三大幅上涨，此前路透社报道称，该公司可能会免受美国正在考虑的对华出口新限制的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-up-hopes-it-will-be-spared-next-round-us-china-chip-fight-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>政府消息人士称，印度钢铁部寻求对更便宜的进口产品进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-steel-ministry-seeks-probe-into-cheaper-imports-government-source-says-2024-07-31/</link><description>一位直接了解此事的政府消息人士周三告诉路透社，印度联邦钢铁部已要求贸易部调查从中国和越南进口的廉价钢铁，目前新德里正努力应对进口增加的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:35:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-steel-ministry-seeks-probe-into-cheaper-imports-government-source-says-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国将取消部分消费级无人机的临时出口管制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adjust-drone-export-control-measures-sept-1-2024-07-31/</link><description>商务部周三表示，中国将从9月1日起调整无人机出口管制，包括取消部分消费级无人机的临时出口管制措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adjust-drone-export-control-measures-sept-1-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>拜登呼吁加大处罚力度、加强管制以应对美国芬太尼危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-calls-bigger-penalties-more-controls-fight-us-fentanyl-crisis-2024-07-31/</link><description>据一位高级政府官员称，总统乔·拜登计划周三呼吁对毒品走私者实施更严厉的处罚，并对药丸压榨商和​​进口商进行更严格的控制，作为应对美国阿片类药物危机的新措施的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-calls-bigger-penalties-more-controls-fight-us-fentanyl-crisis-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国铁木摊贩抗议处罚政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-temu-vendors-protest-over-penalty-policy-2024-07-31/</link><description>一名参与抗议的商家告诉路透社，Temu 上的数百名中国卖家抗议该公司施加的难以忍受的高额罚款，这是与低成本竞争对手 Shein 进行激烈价格竞争的新迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:42:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-temu-vendors-protest-over-penalty-policy-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>欧莱雅首席执行官、投资者摆脱中国疲软的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-ceo-expects-slightly-negative-h2-growth-china-2024-07-31/</link><description>欧莱雅首席执行官 Nicolas Hieronimus 周三表示，中国美容市场下半年将略有下滑，并补充说，尽管季度销售低于预期，但这家法国公司并不依赖市场增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-ceo-expects-slightly-negative-h2-growth-china-2024-07-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>